      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $18,900, this vehicle is in fair overall condition and should be considered a decent driver with visible age and wear. It runs and drives, but buyers should expect cosmetic imperfections and the possibility of some maintenance or repairs depending on their standards and intended use. The interior and exterior are presentable enough for regular use, though not especially clean or standout, and it is best suited for someone looking for an affordable vehicle rather than a showroom-quality one.",
