    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition example that looks usable overall but clearly shows its age. Expect visible cosmetic wear, blemishes, and imperfections around the exterior, along with an interior that has been used and is not show-quality. This is the kind of car that can be enjoyed as a driver, but it will not satisfy someone looking for a particularly clean or highly sorted example. Priced fairly for its condition and best suited for a buyer who wants an approachable, presentable car with some wear already factored in.",
