    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers dependable transportation at an easy entry price. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical choice for buyers seeking simple, low-cost motoring, a project opportunity, or an inexpensive second vehicle. A strong value for someone who prioritizes budget over perfection.",
