    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car is being sold as a budget-friendly runner/project and is priced accordingly. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a straightforward, honest car that could be a great fit for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a first fixer-upper, or something to tinker with on the weekends. If you appreciate value and don\u2019t mind giving a car a little TLC, this one could be a really smart buy.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project car with solid bones and plenty of upside for the next owner. The engine pulls through the rev range, the drivetrain feels mechanically honest, and it has the kind of usable platform that makes a great budget build, shop runner, or weekend revival candidate. Not a showpiece, but it presents as a complete, straightforward vehicle with real potential for someone who appreciates a driver-focused machine and doesn\u2019t mind giving it the attention it deserves. A compelling entry point for an enthusiast looking for value and capability over cosmetics.",
      "price": 6400.0,
